@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8000

### Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Non-secret provider config
GET {{baseUrl}}/ai/config

### Structured recipe importer
POST {{baseUrl}}/ai/import-recipe
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Lemon beans: warm canned beans with lemon juice and olive oil. Serve.",
  "source": "demo fixture"
}

### Ask My Cookbook over saved recipes
# Requires COOKBOOK_DB_PATH to point at a demo SQLite DB with saved recipes.
POST {{baseUrl}}/ai/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "What saved recipe uses lemon?",
  "limit": 2
}

### Local dataset search
# Requires RECIPE_DATASET_DIR to point at a demo folder containing 13k-recipes.csv.
GET {{baseUrl}}/dataset/search?q=lemon&limit=2&dataset_limit=5

### Dataset Ask/RAG with citations
# Requires RECIPE_DATASET_DIR to point at a demo folder containing 13k-recipes.csv.
POST {{baseUrl}}/dataset/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "What indexed recipe uses lemon?",
  "limit": 1,
  "dataset_limit": 5
}

### Saved-recipe meal planning
# Requires COOKBOOK_DB_PATH to point at a demo SQLite DB with saved recipes.
POST {{baseUrl}}/ai/meal-plan
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "days": 1,
  "meals_per_day": 1,
  "preferences": "lemon",
  "candidate_limit": 2
}
